items.title: Stock Market Today: Middle East war, Oil prices, US jobless claims, FIIs

items.title: Shein likely to hold informal investor meet ahead of planned London IPO
items.description: Shein confidentially filed papers with Britain's markets regulator in early June, kicking off the process for a potential London listing by the company later in the year

items.title: Swiggy gets shareholder nod to use provision to upsize IPO fresh issue
items.description: Swiggy's original IPO size eked out NTPC Green Energy's $1.2 billion public offering filing to be the largest in the country this year
